caption.body: For our exhibition “Flying the Freedom Birds: Airlines and the Vietnam War,” we interviewed several flight attendants about their experiences serving on commercial airliners under contract by the U.S. Air Force Military Airlift Command (MAC) during the Vietnam War. Check out the first of a three-part video series: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zmb7JdyzYFI
